Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.72,0:02:00.98,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}心の声は　閉じたままで
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.18,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}あふれそうなCry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.23,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}Lost in the noise, drowning inside
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.58,0:02:09.11,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}But I won't break, I will never lose myself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.24,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}So rise again, I find myself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.24,0:02:15.95,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}僕だけの魔法　探していた
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.95,0:02:18.36,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}数えきれない　絶望も
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.87,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}崩れ落ちた　理想も
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.42,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}一振りの勇気だけ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.05,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}Believers, going back, back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.05,0:02:32.40,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}もう　何千何万回の苦難も　恐れない
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.08,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}ただ　そこに君がいるから
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.18,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}I'm going back, back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.52,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}解き放て　さあどんな未来も
